# H-27: Crafting Upgrade stale-recipe dupe — suggested fix

Paths are relative to the decompiled source tree in this repo. Apply the equivalent change in the upstream `SophisticatedCore` Fabric sources before building a fixed jar.

## Patch: CraftingUpgradeContainer.java

Two changes:
1. In `updateCraftingResult`, clear the match caches on the empty-input path.
2. In `selectCraftingResult`, re-validate the chosen recipe against the current craft matrix before materialising the result slot.

